text: Muhammad Qasim Khan (; born 6 July 1959) is a Pakistani jurist who is the 50th and current Chief Justice of the Lahore High Court since 19 March 2020. He is a relative of PMLN leader Daniyal Aziz. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Judges of the Lahore High Court Category:Pakistani judges
title: Muhammad Qasim Khan
